---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About - Ross Starkey"
  description="Commercial 787 pilot, entrepreneur, and builder. Learn about my journey from aviation to building multiple businesses."
>
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-8">
      About Me
    </h1>

    <div class="space-y-8">
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-teal-500/10 to-transparent border border-gray-800 rounded-lg p-8">
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
          I'm a commercial airline pilot flying the Boeing 787 Dreamliner on long-haul international routes.
          But aviation is just one part of my story. I'm also an entrepreneur, building businesses and products
          while cruising at 40,000 feet.
        </p>
      </div>

      <section class="space-y-6">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6">The Journey</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
          My passion for aviation started early, and I've spent years building my career in commercial aviation.
          Flying the 787 has given me a unique perspective on life, work, and the possibilities that come with
          combining technical expertise with entrepreneurial drive.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
          Between flights, I've built RepPilot, a SaaS platform helping businesses manage online reviews,
          run an SEO agency, invest in property, and create content sharing what I've learned along the way.
          Each venture teaches me something new about business, technology, and building things people actually need.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-6">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6">What Drives Me</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-gray-900/50 border border-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Aviation Excellence</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400">
              Flying one of the most advanced aircraft in the sky requires precision, continuous learning,
              and operational excellence. These principles carry over into everything I build.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-900/50 border border-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Building Products</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400">
              I love creating solutions to real problems. Whether it's automating review management or
              optimizing websites for search, I focus on delivering genuine value.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-900/50 border border-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Leveraging AI</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400">
              AI has transformed how fast we can build. I'm using the latest tools to create products,
              content, and solutions at a pace that wasn't possible before.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-900/50 border border-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Building in Public</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400">
              Sharing the journey, lessons learned, and insights on YouTube and through writing.
              Transparency and helping others succeed drives me forward.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-6">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Skills & Expertise</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-teal-400 mb-3">Aviation</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-400">
              <li>• Boeing 787 Type Rating</li>
              <li>• Long-haul Operations</li>
              <li>• International Routes</li>
              <li>• Flight Training</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-teal-400 mb-3">Technology</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-400">
              <li>• SaaS Development</li>
              <li>• AI Integration</li>
              <li>• Web Development</li>
              <li>• Automation</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-teal-400 mb-3">Business</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-400">
              <li>• SEO Strategy</li>
              <li>• Property Investment</li>
              <li>• Content Creation</li>
              <li>• Product Management</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="bg-gray-900/50 border border-gray-800 rounded-lg p-8 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Let's Connect</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-400 mb-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Always interested in connecting with fellow entrepreneurs, pilots, or anyone building interesting things.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="px-6 py-3 bg-teal-500 text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-teal-600 transition-colors font-medium"
          >
            Get In Touch
          </a>
          <a
            href="/ventures"
            class="px-6 py-3 border-2 border-gray-700 text-gray-300 rounded-lg hover:border-teal-500 hover:text-teal-400 transition-all font-medium"
          >
            View My Ventures
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
